  <title>USB Redirection</title>

  <p><sys>USB</sys> is a universal hardware bus protocol used to plug any king
  of devices to your computer. <sys>USB</sys> redirection permits to make your
  devices plugged to your local computer available to the machines your
  connected to in <app>Boxes</app>, for instance, your pen-drive or your
  webcam as directly connected on the remote computer.</p>

